tags.name: ctd
tags.description:
The Comparative Toxicogenomics Database (CTD) is an open-source database that provides manually curated information about chemical-gene/protein, chemical-disease, and gene-disease relationships, with additional support for the curated relationships provided by functional and pathway data.

**Version:** b95856ba1051bfc2
